coordinates.MLFeatureShortDescription: Normalised coordiantes (relative to the image size) for each of the bounding boxes (x,y,w,h).

confidence.MLFeatureShortDescription: Confidence derived for each of the bounding boxes.

confidenceThreshold.MLFeatureShortDescription: Remove bounding boxes below this threshold (confidences should be nonnegative).

iouThreshold.MLFeatureShortDescription: This defines the radius of suppression.
